AgenticSTS — monorepo licensing
================================

This repository is a monorepo with three components under different licenses.
Each component carries its own full license text; this root file is the map.

  AgenticSTS/        Apache License 2.0          — see AgenticSTS/LICENSE
                     (the Python agent: decision engine, memory, skills, tooling,
                      scripts, leaderboard, docs)

  AgenticSTS-Mod/    GNU AGPL v3.0               — see AgenticSTS-Mod/LICENSE
                     (the C# game mod; a fork of CharTyr/STS2-Agent, whose AGPL
                      terms are inherited)

  AgenticSTS-Data/   CC BY 4.0                   — see AgenticSTS-Data/LICENSE
                     (released run archive, frozen L4/L5 store snapshots)

Root-level files (README.md, NOTICE, CITATION.cff, docs at the repository root)
are licensed under Apache License 2.0, identical to AgenticSTS/LICENSE.

The Apache-2.0 grant on AgenticSTS/ does NOT extend to AgenticSTS-Mod/: if you
distribute or run a modified mod, AGPL-3.0 obligations apply. Third-party and
non-redistributed content (verbatim game data, decompiled extracts) is covered
in NOTICE and AgenticSTS/data/knowledge/README.md and is regenerated locally
rather than shipped.

A full copy of the Apache License 2.0 text is at AgenticSTS/LICENSE.
